  note      = {Mach probe measurement;peripheral plasma rotation evolution;L-H transition;ITB decay;TUMAN-3M tokamak;sheared plasma rotation;turbulent transport suppression;toroidal rotation velocity evolution;poloidal rotation velocity evolution;plasma edge;four-tip movable Mach probe;plasma confinement;H-mode transition;peripheral transport barrier formation;transient internal transport barrier;ohmic heating scenario;closed flux surface;scrape-off layer;core plasmas;radial electric field;density gradient;edge transport barrier region;transient ITB scenario;plasma density profile;plasma temperature profile;},
