  note      = {broadband short-pulse reflectometry;plasma density diagnosis;magnetic-field profiles;numerical simulations;ultra-short-pulse reflectometry;Maxwell's equations;ordinary mode propagation;group delay;electron density profile;extraordinary waves;cutoff relation;electron density;magnetic field;X-mode reflectometry simulation packages;O-mode reflectometry simulation packages;CORSICA comprehensive plasma modelling;DIII-D tokamak;SSPX spheromak;},
