	is known as CORSICA 1.0); (2) coupling the core transport code to
	a 2-D edge transport code (UEDGE); and (3) coupling the transport
	codes to turbulence simulation codes. Progress in all three of these
	areas will be discussed, including: early results from CORSICA 1.0;
