  pages     = {83 - 93},
  volume    = {32},
  abstract  = {Experimental results are presented that verify the formerly predicted
	possibility of the formation of a closed, spheromak-like magnetic
	configuration (SLMC) by the natural magnetic field of a plasma focus
	discharge. The model is based on the self-generated transformation
	of a toroidal (i.e., azimuthal) magnetic field into a poloidal one.
