	from 3% to 8% and a volume averaged energy confinement time &lang;&tau;<sub>E</sub>&rang;&gt;
	between 14 and 35 &mu;sec; while the S-1 spheromak has &lang;&beta;&rang;
	between 15% and 40% and &lang;&tau;<sub>E</sub>&rang; ranging from
	30 to 70 &mu;sec},
