  note      = {ideal MHD stability limits;PROTO-SPHERA experiment;START vacuum vessel;hydrogen force-free screw pinch;standard spherical tokamak;central screw pinch current;aspect ratio;flux core spheromak;spherical torus toroidal current;resistive instability;numerical code;magnetic configurations;open magnetic field lines;current 60 kA;size 70 cm;current 120 kA to 240 kA;},
