  number    = {2-3},
  pages     = {69 - 80},
  volume    = {23},
  abstract  = {The TITAN reversed-field-pinch (RFP) fusion-reactor study has two
	objectives: to determine the technical feasibility and key developmental
	issues for an RFP fusion reactor operating at high power density;
	and to determine the potential economic (cost of electricity), operational
	(maintenance and availability), safety and environmental features
