  note      = {spheromak physics;high-speed imaging;magnetic diagnostics;double frame capability;transient plasma column;toroidal flux;poloidal flux;CORSICA;magnetohydrodynamic equilibrium;elongation measurement;velocity measurement;cathode patterns;pressure gradients;magnetic-field polarity;magnetic probes;current level;toroidal mode number;plasma discharge;},
