	flows. Field reversed configurations (FRCs) are in this class. Both
	classes admit arbitrarily large equilibria. Both classes occupy certain
	&ldquo;allowed&rdquo; regions in &ldquo;helicity space,&rdquo; a
	two-dimensional parameter map with the electron and ion helicities
