	region on the basis of simulation results; in that study the SCT
	is decelerated not only by the magnetic pressure force but also by
	the magnetic tension force. However, since both ends of the target
	magnetic field are fixed on the boundary wall in the simulation,
	the deceleration caused by the magnetic tension force would be overestimated.
