	magnetic field propagate with the Alfven velocity. In addition, by
	carrying out the simulation with the torus domain, it is confirmed
	that the theoretical model can be applied to estimate the penetration
	depth of the SCT under such conditions. The dependence of the injection
	position (side injection and top/bottom injection) on the penetration
