  note      = {spherical tokamak;plasma center column;low aspect ratio toroidal pinches;reactor engineering design;material center post;biased electrodes;plasma current;toroidal magnetic field;toroidal field coils;magnetic helicity injection;auxiliary current drive;RF heating;neutral beam injection;Taylor-relaxed plasma;flux amplification factor;plasma shaping;plasma elongation;vacuum bias magnetic flux;spheromak;},
