  note      = {3D structure;magnetic clouds;flux ropes;toroids;propagating spheromaks;initial internal field;ambient interplanetary magnetic field interaction;poloidal field;oblate shape;solar wind momentum interaction;magnetic field line draping;spacecraft crossings;magnetic cloud observations;double flux rope crossings exclusion;},
