	instability, whereas the ordering &Omega;/&omega;<sub>A</sub>~&epsiv;<sup>3/2</sup>
	represents a transition regime where the stabilizing effect of the
	rotation competes with the drive from the internal kink instability.
	Kinetic behavior along the field lines is expected to influence this
	stabilization mechanism, as it depends on the adiabatic index &Gamma;},
